Undergraduate Student Affairs

Latest News and Updates •  Contact Us Here • Division of Career Pathways
 




Type of Advising


Topics


Availability


Contact:






Live Chat

Quick, General Questions
Weeks 1-10
 Academic Advisors & Peer Academic Advisors  



Ucounsel

File Submission, Policy/Procedures, Academic Advising, Straightforward Questions
Response: 3 - 4 Business Days
Academic Advisors & Peer Academic Advisors



Drop-In Advising

Policy/Procedures, Course Scheduling, General Advising
Weeks 1-10

Peer Academic Advisors (Week 1-10)
Academic Advisors (Week 0-1 & 7-9)




Scheduled Appointment

 More complicated issues or questions
Weeks 3-6, 10
Academic Advisors & Peer Academic Advisors



 
»Live Chat: 
Online live chat service available to ask general advising questions. Meant for quick questions requiring a more immediate response.

»Email: 
Submit a Ucounsel Form and we will respond to you in 3 - 4 business days.
»﻿PAA Drop-In: 
Our PAAs are available for any questions you may have about:


ICS policies
Majors/Minors
Change of Major
General Education
Degree Requirements
Course Scheduling

And Much More! Get to know our 2021-2022 PAAs! 

»Appointments: 


Current UCI Students: Visit https://appointments.web.uci.edu/ and select ICS Undergraduate Student Affairs
Non-UCI students: Please call (949) 824-5156 to schedule an appointment. 



