Scheduled Appointment

 More complicated issues or questions
Weeks 3-6, 10
Academic Advisors & Peer Academic Advisors



 
»Live Chat: 
Online live chat service available to ask general advising questions. Meant for quick questions requiring a more immediate response.

»Email: 
Submit a Ucounsel Form and we will respond to you in 3 - 4 business days.
»﻿PAA Drop-In: 
Our PAAs are available for any questions you may have about:


ICS policies
Majors/Minors
Change of Major
General Education
Degree Requirements
Course Scheduling

And Much More! Get to know our 2021-2022 PAAs! 

»Appointments: 


Current UCI Students: Visit https://appointments.web.uci.edu/ and select ICS Undergraduate Student Affairs
Non-UCI students: Please call (949) 824-5156 to schedule an appointment. 



